column5: Does anyone know of any guides that know EAGLE,LAC SEULor WABIGOON lakes.Going up june12-24,bringing own boat, 3 people.Any help? thanks PUKE

For a excellent Eagle Lake guide, go to www.birchdalelodge.comthe guides name here is Greg Bretsch. I lost his email address so this is the only way I can think of you hooking up with him.Tell him I sent you !Good FishenRob Carlson
